{"lang":"ja","stage":5,"title":"everyday sentences, growing","sentences":[{"t":"自分がどこにいるかわかんない。","en":"I don't know where I am.","r":"Jibun ga doko ni iru ka wakannai.","a":"n_7f38240c4418.mp3"},{"t":"どこにあるかわかんない。","en":"I don't know where it is.","r":"Doko ni aru ka wakannai.","a":"n_11e326491532.mp3"},{"t":"彼女どこ出身？","en":"Where is she from?","r":"Kanojo doko shusshin?","a":"n_f9f51c07e100.mp3"},{"t":"遅れそうなんだ。","en":"I'm running late.","r":"Okuresō na n da.","a":"n_421c4bec1e3e.mp3"},{"t":"ちょっと痛い。","en":"It hurts a little.","r":"Chotto itai.","a":"n_e790c3b8a204.mp3"},{"t":"どこも痛くないよ。","en":"Nothing hurts.","r":"Doko mo itakunai yo.","a":"n_9f0c47355010.mp3"},{"t":"今日は時間ないんだ。","en":"I don't have time today.","r":"Kyō wa jikan nai n da.","a":"n_9f8128766e95.mp3"},{"t":"ここの出身じゃないんだ。","en":"I'm not from here.","r":"Koko no shusshin ja nai n da.","a":"n_4d7b0692dbc8.mp3"},{"t":"どうしたらいいかわかんない。","en":"I don't know what to do.","r":"Dō shitara ii ka wakannai.","a":"n_605478ebd8eb.mp3"},{"t":"ちょっと疲れた。","en":"I'm a little tired.","r":"Chotto tsukareta.","a":"n_837b3fe64f2b.mp3"},{"t":"今日はすごく疲れた。","en":"I'm really tired today.","r":"Kyō wa sugoku tsukareta.","a":"n_a02e4b32aa59.mp3"},{"t":"君の家いいね。","en":"I like your house.","r":"Kimi no ie ii ne.","a":"n_5a1767f538d7.mp3"},{"t":"今日はなにもしないよ。","en":"Today I'm doing nothing.","r":"Kyō wa nani mo shinai yo.","a":"n_0f181a0c229f.mp3"},{"t":"全部自分でやるんだ。","en":"I do everything by myself.","r":"Zenbu jibun de yaru n da.","a":"n_bbcca8941bfa.mp3"},{"t":"そういうことはしないものだよ。","en":"You don't do that.","r":"Sō iu koto wa shinai mono da yo.","a":"n_81cb3012588a.mp3"},{"t":"家に帰りたい。","en":"I want to go home.","r":"Ie ni kaeritai.","a":"n_42b46bc4abcc.mp3"},{"t":"今日何曜日？","en":"What day is it today?","r":"Kyō nan'yōbi?","a":"n_077a35756630.mp3"},{"t":"コーヒー買いたい。","en":"I want to buy a coffee.","r":"Kōhī kaitai.","a":"n_10cf69d74d52.mp3"},{"t":"今日なにしたい？","en":"What do you want to do today?","r":"Kyō nani shitai?","a":"n_2ce3588cc4f8.mp3"},{"t":"なにか食べに行こう。","en":"Let's go eat something.","r":"Nanika tabe ni ikō.","a":"n_e27cbfec3205.mp3"},{"t":"彼は友達じゃないよ。","en":"He's not my friend.","r":"Kare wa tomodachi ja nai yo.","a":"n_0c130fc674c6.mp3"},{"t":"彼は友達だよ。","en":"He's my friend.","r":"Kare wa tomodachi da yo.","a":"n_9fc479151ff8.mp3"},{"t":"こちら友達だよ。","en":"This is my friend.","r":"Kochira tomodachi da yo.","a":"n_8961d02f83c9.mp3"},{"t":"ご飯は私が作るよ。","en":"I make the food.","r":"Gohan wa watashi ga tsukuru yo.","a":"n_136256213128.mp3"},{"t":"ご飯どう？","en":"How's the food?","r":"Gohan dō?","a":"n_0e3faeb48267.mp3"},{"t":"これ全部でいくら？","en":"How much is all of this?","r":"Kore zenbu de ikura?","a":"n_3188379a7a51.mp3"},{"t":"バスいくら？","en":"How much is the bus?","r":"Basu ikura?","a":"n_363ac76e84d3.mp3"},{"t":"気分が良くないんだ。","en":"I don't feel well.","r":"Kibun ga yokunai n da.","a":"n_e6355c53b592.mp3"},{"t":"もう少し良くなったよ。","en":"I feel better now.","r":"Mō sukoshi yoku natta yo.","a":"n_9293501d6481.mp3"},{"t":"で、君はだれ？","en":"And who are you?","r":"De, kimi wa dare?","a":"n_bcf3120c92f5.mp3"},{"t":"バス停近いよ。","en":"The bus is close.","r":"Basu-tei chikai yo.","a":"n_cde3296a575d.mp3"},{"t":"今日はお金あんまりないんだ。","en":"I have a little money today.","r":"Kyō wa okane anmari nai n da.","a":"n_ea26ff53b89b.mp3"},{"t":"それ大金だね。","en":"That's a lot of money.","r":"Sore taikin da ne.","a":"n_b6abb9a097dd.mp3"},{"t":"なにか食べるものある？","en":"What is there to eat?","r":"Nanika taberu mono aru?","a":"n_22257730603e.mp3"},{"t":"行くの、行かないの？","en":"Are you going or not?","r":"Iku no, ikanai no?","a":"n_719690173128.mp3"},{"t":"今日はなにもしなかった。","en":"I didn't do anything today.","r":"Kyō wa nani mo shinakatta.","a":"n_cff60d64341d.mp3"},{"t":"昨日はなにもしなかった。","en":"Yesterday I did nothing.","r":"Kinō wa nani mo shinakatta.","a":"n_bcc7250ae3a9.mp3"},{"t":"昨日なにもしなかったよ。","en":"I didn't do anything yesterday.","r":"Kinō nani mo shinakatta yo.","a":"n_3c10511abac6.mp3"},{"t":"キッチンにいるよ。","en":"I'm in the kitchen.","r":"Kitchin ni iru yo.","a":"n_aee0cd81ae23.mp3"},{"t":"キッチンはこっちだよ。","en":"The kitchen is here.","r":"Kitchin wa kotchi da yo.","a":"n_82f1b9a97576.mp3"},{"t":"キッチンどこ？","en":"Where's the kitchen?","r":"Kitchin doko?","a":"n_9a4c0370a719.mp3"},{"t":"お医者さんどこ？","en":"Where's the doctor?","r":"Oisha-san doko?","a":"n_e090a4a94fd3.mp3"},{"t":"今日病院行くんだ。","en":"I'm going to the doctor today.","r":"Kyō byōin iku n da.","a":"n_084e827f06b6.mp3"},{"t":"病院行かなきゃ。","en":"I need to go to the doctor.","r":"Byōin ikanakya.","a":"n_4a59bbf394bd.mp3"},{"t":"すごく具合悪いんだ。","en":"I feel really bad.","r":"Sugoku guai warui n da.","a":"n_68ba6e136830.mp3"},{"t":"コーヒーお願いします。","en":"I'd like a coffee.","r":"Kōhī onegai shimasu.","a":"n_bc9be953ceab.mp3"},{"t":"スマホどこ？","en":"Where's my phone?","r":"Sumaho doko?","a":"n_ffb8aa2965d3.mp3"},{"t":"よく見えないよ。","en":"I can't see you well.","r":"Yoku mienai yo.","a":"n_9034d50b6d9b.mp3"},{"t":"また後でね。","en":"I'll see you later.","r":"Mata ato de ne.","a":"n_55b7e1d3bac1.mp3"},{"t":"今日はゆっくり起きるんだ。","en":"Today I'm getting up late.","r":"Kyō wa yukkuri okiru n da.","a":"n_d9d9233757c6.mp3"},{"t":"明日は早く起きるんだ。","en":"Tomorrow I'm getting up early.","r":"Ashita wa hayaku okiru n da.","a":"n_3864b2e921ca.mp3"},{"t":"なに頼むか迷うな。","en":"I don't know what to order.","r":"Nani tanomu ka mayou na.","a":"n_4bfecabe28c9.mp3"},{"t":"なに頼む？","en":"What are you going to order?","r":"Nani tanomu?","a":"n_1d3989770dbe.mp3"},{"t":"寝たい気分だな。","en":"I feel like sleeping.","r":"Netai kibun da na.","a":"n_7678c4a74390.mp3"},{"t":"出かけたい気分？","en":"Do you feel like going out?","r":"Dekaketai kibun?","a":"n_d8b9a67b2a66.mp3"},{"t":"水いくら？","en":"How much is the water?","r":"Mizu ikura?","a":"n_8b59b1eefd49.mp3"},{"t":"キッチンにいるよ。","en":"We're in the kitchen.","r":"Kitchin ni iru yo.","a":"n_aee0cd81ae23.mp3"},{"t":"もっと学びたいな。","en":"I'd like to learn more.","r":"Motto manabitai na.","a":"n_9d841d3fe2cd.mp3"},{"t":"それはやめたほうがいいよ。","en":"You shouldn't do that.","r":"Sore wa yameta hō ga ii yo.","a":"n_1725ab335401.mp3"},{"t":"そんなに働きすぎないほうがいいよ。","en":"You shouldn't work so much.","r":"Sonna ni hatarakisuginai hō ga ii yo.","a":"n_df2ac821eb2d.mp3"},{"t":"なんで来ないの？","en":"Why aren't you coming?","r":"Nande konai no?","a":"n_03b6f9bca9cf.mp3"},{"t":"何時に来るの？","en":"What time are you coming?","r":"Nan-ji ni kuru no?","a":"n_cbd2e9e7ad4c.mp3"},{"t":"近いの、遠いの？","en":"Is it close or far?","r":"Chikai no, tōi no?","a":"n_1e2ae92533bd.mp3"},{"t":"電車は安いよ。","en":"The train is cheap.","r":"Densha wa yasui yo.","a":"n_44d5b41bf656.mp3"},{"t":"駅は遠いよ。","en":"The train is far.","r":"Eki wa tōi yo.","a":"n_04dc6b0e1ed2.mp3"},{"t":"もっと安いのある？","en":"Do you have anything cheaper?","r":"Motto yasui no aru?","a":"n_c8572c755952.mp3"},{"t":"また私だよ。","en":"It's me again.","r":"Mata watashi da yo.","a":"n_cb006b80e82a.mp3"},{"t":"五分で着くよ。","en":"I'll be there in five minutes.","r":"Go-fun de tsuku yo.","a":"n_3af30da21736.mp3"},{"t":"君と出かけるの好きだよ。","en":"I like going out with you.","r":"Kimi to dekakeru no suki da yo.","a":"n_ca54ba7dee8e.mp3"},{"t":"君と一緒に行きたいな。","en":"I'd like to go with you.","r":"Kimi to issho ni ikitai na.","a":"n_6dfeff2476e7.mp3"},{"t":"君と一緒にスペイン語学びたい。","en":"I want to learn Spanish with you.","r":"Kimi to issho ni Supein-go manabitai.","a":"n_7151f1459e3a.mp3"},{"t":"明日は勉強するよ。","en":"Tomorrow I'm going to study.","r":"Ashita wa benkyō suru yo.","a":"n_f26b5449954b.mp3"},{"t":"だれもなにも言ってくれなかった。","en":"Nobody told me anything.","r":"Dare mo nani mo itte kurenakatta.","a":"n_694750d91dcb.mp3"},{"t":"いつ言われたの？","en":"When did he tell you?","r":"Itsu iwareta no?","a":"n_c14687c34289.mp3"},{"t":"いつから痛いの？","en":"How long has it been hurting?","r":"Itsu kara itai no?","a":"n_90c053a59b75.mp3"},{"t":"今日は早く寝るよ。","en":"I'm going to bed early today.","r":"Kyō wa hayaku neru yo.","a":"n_e93a416cf5ea.mp3"},{"t":"街までどうやって行くの？","en":"How do I get downtown?","r":"Machi made dō yatte iku no?","a":"n_85a9529fa76a.mp3"},{"t":"なんで悲しいの？","en":"Why are you sad?","r":"Nande kanashii no?","a":"n_24208d4949e4.mp3"},{"t":"彼、私のことなんて言ってた？","en":"What did he say about me?","r":"Kare, watashi no koto nan te itteta?","a":"n_0daee3896737.mp3"},{"t":"同じのがほしい。","en":"I want the same thing.","r":"Onaji no ga hoshii.","a":"n_de211fab4b81.mp3"},{"t":"質問していい？","en":"Can I ask a question?","r":"Shitsumon shite ii?","a":"n_f71760736d34.mp3"},{"t":"彼っていつも同じこと聞くんだよね。","en":"He always asks the same thing.","r":"Kare tte itsumo onaji koto kiku n da yo ne.","a":"n_9fa9712a69e2.mp3"},{"t":"だれが私のこと聞いてるの？","en":"Who's asking about me?","r":"Dare ga watashi no koto kiiteru no?","a":"n_da69a41186fc.mp3"},{"t":"なんて言えばいいかわかんない。","en":"I don't know what to say.","r":"Nan te ieba ii ka wakannai.","a":"n_f2935856442a.mp3"},{"t":"今日は運動しないよ。","en":"I'm not working out today.","r":"Kyō wa undō shinai yo.","a":"n_78f6f0c672ed.mp3"},{"t":"もっと運動したいな。","en":"I want to work out more.","r":"Motto undō shitai na.","a":"n_3064924354b2.mp3"},{"t":"私の友達知ってる？","en":"Do you know my friend?","r":"Watashi no tomodachi shitteru?","a":"n_0dcb94d19398.mp3"},{"t":"今払うね。","en":"I'm going to pay now.","r":"Ima harau ne.","a":"n_aa8ae32de3dd.mp3"},{"t":"そんなに払いたくないな。","en":"I don't want to pay that much.","r":"Sonna ni haraitakunai na.","a":"n_195d8204c0ab.mp3"},{"t":"タクシー来たよ。","en":"The taxi is here.","r":"Takushī kita yo.","a":"n_0bad10876863.mp3"},{"t":"十分で着くよ。","en":"I'll be there in ten minutes.","r":"Jippun de tsuku yo.","a":"n_25128e18517a.mp3"},{"t":"十時に着くよ。","en":"I arrive at ten.","r":"Jū-ji ni tsuku yo.","a":"n_5c1bff8e947b.mp3"},{"t":"それ私の名前じゃないよ。","en":"That's not my name.","r":"Sore watashi no namae ja nai yo.","a":"n_6b3c411ae264.mp3"},{"t":"パーティー行くよ。","en":"I'm going to the party.","r":"Pātī iku yo.","a":"n_b4f3b9b6a543.mp3"}]}